  </section>
  
<!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-950 px-6 py-24 text-white sm:py-32">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-[420px] w-[420px] rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 blur-[130px]">
      </div>

      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-[420px] w-[420px] rounded-full bg-blue-600/10 blur-[130px]">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="grid gap-14 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:gap-20">
        <div data-reveal="left">
          <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-cyan-300">
            What guides us
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-5 text-3xl font-black tracking-[-0.03em] sm:text-5xl">
            Technology built around trust and human dignity.
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
            Healthcare technology must do more than operate efficiently. It must
            protect people, strengthen institutions, and remain accessible to
            the communities it is designed to serve.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <article
            data-reveal="scale"
            data-pointer-glow
            style="--reveal-delay: 0ms;"
            class="about-interactive-card rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] p-7 backdrop-blur transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-cyan-300/30 hover:bg-white/[0.08]"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-black text-cyan-300">01</span>

            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-black">
              Patient first
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
              Every workflow and feature begins with the safety, dignity, and
              wellbeing of the patient.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article
            data-reveal="scale"
            data-pointer-glow
            style="--reveal-delay: 100ms;"
            class="about-interactive-card rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] p-7 backdrop-blur transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-cyan-300/30 hover:bg-white/[0.08]"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-black text-cyan-300">02</span>

            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-black">
              Privacy by design
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
