          <article
            data-reveal="scale"
            data-pointer-glow
            style="--reveal-delay: 200ms;"
            class="about-interactive-card rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] p-7 backdrop-blur transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-cyan-300/30 hover:bg-white/[0.08]"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-black text-cyan-300">03</span>

            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-black">
              Inclusive innovation
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
              Our solutions are designed for different levels of connectivity,
              infrastructure, and digital literacy.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article
            data-reveal="scale"
            data-pointer-glow
            style="--reveal-delay: 300ms;"
            class="about-interactive-card rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] p-7 backdrop-blur transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-cyan-300/30 hover:bg-white/[0.08]"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-black text-cyan-300">04</span>

            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-black">
              Connected progress
